      • convertMethods

        public static void convertMethods(UmlElement element,
                                  CodeElement codeElement,
                                  TemporaryModel tmpModel)
        Static method to convert UmlOperations of an UmlElement to CodeMethods and adding them to the CodeElement.
        Delegates the conversion of CodeParameters to the ParameterConverter
        Delegates the conversion of CodeTemplateParameters to the TemplateParameterConverter
        Parameters:
        element - the UmlElement which UmlOperation should be converted
        codeElement - the CodeElement to which the converted CodeMethods should be added to
        tmpModel - the TemporaryModel containing the maps to add temporary CodeTemplateBindings and converted CodeTemplateParameters to

      • getOperationReturnParameter

        public static UmlParameter getOperationReturnParameter(UmlOperation operation)
        Returns the UmlParameter of the given UmlOperation with UmlParameterDirection.RETURN.
        Parameters:
        operation - the UmlOperation to get the return UmlParameter of
        Returns:
        the UmlParameter with UmlParameterDirection.RETURN or null if there is none.
